chapter.para:
   (1)connect, disconnect, tap, or interfere or tamper with any of the canals, springs, reservoirs,
tunnels, mounds, dams, plugs, fire hydrants, mains, pipes, conduits, connections, taps,
valves, engines, or machinery belonging to the City;

   (2)connect with any canal, spring, reservoir, tunnel, mound, dam, plug, fire hydrant, main,
pipe, conduit, connection, tap, valve, engine, or machinery for the purpose of using or
wasting water;
